# tpd/

This directory contains the Technical Product Design (TPD) documentation template and framework for the Intent project. It provides a comprehensive structure for documenting system architecture, requirements, implementation strategy, and operational procedures through a series of interconnected markdown files.

## Files

- `_technical_product_design.md` -- Main TPD index document with preamble and table of contents
- `_1_introduction.md` -- System purpose, scope, definitions, overview, and references
- `_2_requirements.md` -- Functional and non-functional requirements, constraints, and assumptions
- `_3_architecture.md` -- System and component architecture, data flows, interfaces, and deployment
- `_4_detailed_design.md` -- Component designs, algorithms, data structures, database schema, and APIs
- `_5_implementation_strategy.md` -- Development approach, phases, task breakdown, testing, and deployment strategy
- `_6_deployment_and_operations.md` -- Installation, deployment process, operational procedures, maintenance, and scaling
- `_7_technical_challenges_and_mitigations.md` -- Technical challenges and mitigation strategies
- `_8_appendices.md` -- Glossary, references, specifications, API documentation, and decision records
